"When people are happy to work for a company, feel that they're being heard and that the work they do is productive, they're more committed to making that company successful", says Nina McQueen, vice president of global benefits and employee satisfaction at LinkedIn, which uses both Convercent and Glint.
Investors make a profit when the businesses in their portfolio are doing well; companies are doing well when employees are committed and involved.
If third-party analytics promises to increase employee engagement and engagement, it's no wonder they're getting support.
